queries.sql: SELECT `tbl_arsip`.*, CASE WHEN tbl_user.id_user IS NULL THEN CONCAT(tbl_arsip.nama_user_upload, " (User Dihapus)") ELSE tbl_user.nama_user END as nama_user, `tbl_kategori`.`nama_kategori`, `tbl_dep`.`nama_dep` FROM `tbl_arsip` LEFT JOIN `tbl_user` ON `tbl_user`.`id_user` = `tbl_arsip`.`id_user` LEFT JOIN `tbl_kategori` ON `tbl_kategori`.`id_kategori` = `tbl_arsip`.`id_kategori` LEFT JOIN `tbl_dep` ON `tbl_dep`.`id_dep` = `tbl_arsip`.`id_dep` ORDER BY `tbl_arsip`.`id_arsip` DESC
